# axieST: collect scholars' data every day

# you can customize 
# - 0 0 * * * --> every day at midnight
# - root --> with a specific user with write access in axieST directory
# - /root/axieST_venv --> with your venv directory
# - /opt/axie-scholar-tracker/ --> with your axieST directory
0 0 * * * root /root/axieST_venv/bin/python /opt/axie-scholar-tracker/axieST.py
